\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

 is a subset of 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

, the set of all images, 
\begin_inset Formula $\{T(x):x\text{ is in }S\}$
\end_inset

 is called 
\series bold
the image
\series default
 of 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

